Authenticated SCMP
 
This commit adds authentication capabilities for SCMP packets to the SCION infrastructure.
 
Changes:
 -Add Security extension in Python and Go
 -Add SCMPAuth extension in Python and Go
 -Add authenticating/verifying capabilities to BR
 -Add Packet buffering capabilities to BR, for packets with missing key
 -Add key sharing between BR and local CS
 -Add key sharing between local and remote CS
 -Modify topology generator to create a SCION Deamon per SCION element in an AS
 -Modify BR to automatically authenticate self created SCMP messages
 
Future updates:
 -More extensive tests
 -Enable Zookeeper keysharing between local CSes
 -Encrypt communication between local CS and BR
 -Verify CertChains
 -Add HashTree signature capability
